title: [River's Rest, Olive Grove]
description: Ancient olive trees, their trunks as thick and rough as the hands of old fishermen, line the pathway.  Lanterns hanging among the thick, grey-green leaves give off a pallid light.  The lanterns in the more distant trees look like fireflies.  Scattered among the trees are a few small, pastel-colored stucco buildings.

Ancient olive trees, their trunks as thick and rough as the hands of old fishermen, line the pathway.  Bright, colorful ribbons and banners are hung among the thick, grey-green leaves.  Scattered among the trees are a few small, pastel-colored stucco buildings.
